                     <interp inst="t17731020-80-off399" type="offenceSubcategory" value="perjury"></interp>
               wilful and corrupt perjury, in an affidavit sworn before the filer of bills in Middlesex, for the purpose of causing 12 l. to be indorsed upon a bill in Middlesex, for the purpose of arresting 
                     <persName id="t17731020-80-person689">
                        John
                         Howell
