               <p>Mr. Marshall. I am filer of the bills in Middlesex: I know the defendant's hand writing; the hand writing subscribed to this affidavit (producing it) is his hand writing: it is the duty of my office to file these affidavits.</p>
               <p>Mr. 
               <persName id="t17731020-80-person690">
                  Thomas
                   Frith
               <interp inst="t17731020-80-person690" type="surname" value="Frith"></interp>
