            . I am clerk to the sheriff of Middlesex's office. (Produces a bill of Middlesex issued against 
               <persName id="t17731020-80-person691">
                  John
                   Howel
               <interp inst="t17731020-80-person691" type="surname" value="Howel"></interp>
